#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.87"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.87:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.87:0.2"
msgid "9. Sativagga"
msgstr "9. Mindfulness"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an8.87:0.3"
msgid "87. Pattanikujjanasutta"
msgstr "87. Turning the Bowl Upside Down"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.345"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: nikkujjeyya → nikujjeyya (mr)
msgctxt "an8.87:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Aṭṭhahi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgatassa upāsakassa ākaṅkhamāno saṃgho "
"pattaṃ nikkujjeyya."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, the Saṅgha may, if it wishes, turn the bowl upside down for a "
"lay follower on eight grounds."

msgctxt "an8.87:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi aṭṭhahi?"
msgstr "What eight?"

#. VAR: avāsāya → anāvāsāya (si, s1-3, pts1)
#. VAR: bhedeti → vibhedeti (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an8.87:1.3"
msgid ""
"Bhikkhūnaṃ alābhāya parisakkati, bhikkhūnaṃ anatthāya parisakkati, "
"bhikkhūnaṃ avāsāya parisakkati, bhikkhū akkosati paribhāsati, bhikkhū "
"bhikkhūhi bhedeti, buddhassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, dhammassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, "
"saṃghassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsati."
msgstr ""
"They try to prevent the mendicants from getting material possessions. They "
"try to harm mendicants. They try to drive mendicants from a monastery. They "
"insult and abuse mendicants. They divide mendicants against each other. They "
"criticize the Buddha, the teaching, and the Saṅgha."

msgctxt "an8.87:1.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhahaṅgehi samannāgatassa upāsakassa ākaṅkhamāno "
"saṃgho pattaṃ nikkujjeyya."
msgstr ""
"The Saṅgha may, if it wishes, turn the bowl upside down for a lay follower "
"on these eight grounds."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.87:2.1"
msgid ""
"Aṭṭhahi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgatassa upāsakassa ākaṅkhamāno saṅgho "
"pattaṃ ukkujjeyya."
msgstr ""
"The Saṅgha may, if it wishes, turn the bowl upright for a lay follower on "
"eight grounds."

msgctxt "an8.87:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi aṭṭhahi?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "an8.87:2.3"
msgid ""
"Na bhikkhūnaṃ alābhāya parisakkati, na bhikkhūnaṃ anatthāya parisakkati, na "
"bhikkhūnaṃ avāsāya parisakkati, na bhikkhū akkosati paribhāsati, na bhikkhū "
"bhikkhūhi bhedeti, buddhassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, dhammassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, "
"saṅghassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati."
msgstr ""
"They don’t try to prevent the mendicants from getting material possessions. "
"They don’t try to harm mendicants. They don’t try to drive mendicants from a "
"monastery. They don’t insult and abuse mendicants. They don’t divide "
"mendicants against each other. They don’t criticize the Buddha, the "
"teaching, and the Saṅgha."

msgctxt "an8.87:2.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhahaṅgehi samannāgatassa upāsakassa ākaṅkhamāno "
"saṅgho pattaṃ ukkujjeyyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"The Saṅgha may, if it wishes, turn the bowl upright for a lay follower on "
"these eight grounds.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.87:2.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
